le/3257308/huawei-founder-ren-zhengfei-focuses-digital-transformation-tech-innovation-meeting-petrochina?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国斡旋的伊朗沙特和平红利为故宫博物院带来稀有展品</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3257269/china-brokered-iran-saudi-peace-dividend-brings-rare-exhibits-palace-museum?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>据观察人士称，全球南方国家越来越愿意在北京举办不受西方影响的展览。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 06:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3257269/china-brokered-iran-saudi-peace-dividend-brings-rare-exhibits-palace-museum?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>韩国正在加速KF-21战斗机的量产，中国不会高兴</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3257066/south-korea-zooming-ahead-mass-production-its-kf-21-fighter-jet-and-china-wont-be-happy?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>专家称，预计北京将首尔大规模生产最新型飞机视为对其军火贸易的“威胁”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 03:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3257066/south-korea-zooming-ahead-mass-production-its-kf-21-fighter-jet-and-china-wont-be-happy?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国的未来取决于微观经济的正确发展</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/comment/china-opinion/article/3256825/chinas-future-depends-it-getting-its-microeconomics-right?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>宏观经济刺激只能提供暂时的提振。中国不再是一个充斥着投机者的充满泡沫的市场，他们为价格过高的产品支付愚蠢的钱。企业必须变革才能繁荣。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 01:30:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/comment/china-opinion/article/3256825/chinas-future-depends-it-getting-its-microeconomics-right?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国的金融新规给“肉汁列车”踩下了刹车，让“贪婪是好事”的时代停止了</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3257250/chinas-new-rules-finance-pull-brakes-gravy-train-bringing-greed-good-era-halt?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国的金融业曾经是随心所欲的，但新的监管规定和官员的指令表明，银行的新角色不再只是简单地追求利润。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 22:00:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3257250/chinas-new-rules-finance-pull-brakes-gravy-train-bringing-greed-good-era-halt?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>第23条国家安全法通过后，美国将对香港官员实施新的签证限制</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3257288/us-put-new-visa-limits-hong-kong-officials-after-article-23-passage?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯将目标锁定在那些被认为“对权利和自由加紧镇压负有责任”的人身上。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 21:08:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3257288/us-put-new-visa-limits-hong-kong-officials-after-article-23-passage?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>巴尔的摩大桥倒塌及其对全球贸易的影响</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3257285/baltimore-bridge-collapse-and-its-impact-global-trade?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>残骸导致美国第九大港口关闭，该港口也是通往中国的重要通道，中国是煤炭的主要消费国，通过该港口运输煤炭。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 18:57:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3257285/baltimore-bridge-collapse-and-its-impact-global-trade?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国领导的团队寻找难以捉摸的引力量子，发现了粒子表现得像引力子的第一个证据</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3257232/china-led-team-seeking-elusive-quantum-gravity-finds-first-evidence-particles-behaving-gravitons?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>来自中国、美国和德国的科学家发现，电子只有在引力子中才会发生自旋，引力子是一种备受追捧的能产生引力的粒子。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 15:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3257232/china-led-team-seeking-elusive-quantum-gravity-finds-first-evidence-particles-behaving-gravitons?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>尽管有习近平的授权，中国央行仍对债券交易保持“谨慎”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3257251/chinas-central-bank-keeps-cautious-bond-trade-despite-xi-jinpings-mandate?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>即使习近平主席要求中国央